channel.title: Server Help
channel.description: I have just started playing private servers again on mopar scape for RS. It used to have User, pass, server IP, port. Now i only have user,pass, server IP? The port isn't there anymore.. :confused: And EVERY server i try to connect too, i have tryed over 30.. Just says a diffrent error each time, i have checked the IP to see if it's right every time.. Anyone fancy being a life saver and telling me what's going on? :D

item.title: Server Help
item.dc:creator: @Ddragonimp Ddragonimp
item.description:
@Ddragonimp wrote:

0_bby_m0ul:

Yes but, :mad: do i type the port number in, it just says, “Username” “Password” “Sever IP” No section to type the port in!

Your issue makes me concerned… you dont specify what client you use and if it is moparscape client its file change port…

Next matter…

If its Delta Ofcourse you can’t connet to those servers they have Enforce client
and another thing they changed your walk/stand emote so you disconnect when you connect…
